      <title>美元连跌推动欧元、英镑创 2024 年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/dollar-s-losing-streak-sends-euro-pound-to-fresh-2024-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元的下跌刺激了其他主要货币的上涨，推动欧元和英镑创下 2024 年新高，因为交易员们开始关注未来的全球利率走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/dollar-s-losing-streak-sends-euro-pound-to-fresh-2024-highs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 16:50:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
