      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 12:24:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储面临美国就业岗位减少多达一百万的局面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/fed-confronts-up-to-a-million-us-jobs-vanishing-in-revision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[截至 3 月份的一年里，美国就业增长可能远低于最初的预期，这可能会加剧人们对美联储降低利率的步伐进一步落后的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/fed-confronts-up-to-a-million-us-jobs-vanishing-in-revision</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
